structure.unit: LEVY AND ASSESSMENT OF PROPERTY TAXES

law.history: Repealed 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 168, sec. 158, effective January 1, 2006. -- Amended 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 85, sec. 182, effective June 20, 2005. -- Created 1956 Ky. Acts ch. 158, sec. 1, effective May 18, 1956.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Life insurance companies to report names and addresses of residents entitled to proceeds of policies left on deposit and subject to right of withdrawal, and beneficiaries of policies taxable under KRS 132.215.
